snippet.title: Amber Heard blocks Johnny Depp's followers on Twitter.
snippet.description:
@AmberHeard blocks #JohnnyDepp's followers on #Twitter.

Amber Laura Heard is an American film and television actress. After a series of small roles in film and television, Heard had her first starring role in the horror film All the Boys Love Mandy Lane.

John Christopher Depp II is an American actor, producer, and musician. He has been nominated for ten Golden Globe Awards, winning one for Best Actor for Sweeney Todd: The Demon Barber of Fleet Street, and has been nominated for three Academy Awards for Best Actor, among other accolades.
